{"title":"MUE_ACV_Stroke","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/MUE - Medicina de Urgencia/MUE_ACV_Stroke.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"ACV / STROKE EN URGENCIAS","guid":"8WY4-ePmSdul14_FQikmiw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"DEFINICIONES Y CLASIFICACIÓN","guid":"KLCsNuT6RLuztJsDGobSKA","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"ACV isquémico (80-85%)","guid":"-pPeBiUHQqmM-EvxYMLgNg","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"→ Oclusión arterial cerebral → isquemia → infarto","guid":"tPorD95uTCWZg3HoqvZj5w","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"→ Subtipos (TOAST)","guid":"ca4FE1BDSq6sOeYnGd6kMw","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"Aterotrombótico (grandes vasos): 25%","guid":"sBL2SdnaRT2F0F5LfT9NJA","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"Cardioembólico: 25% (FA principal causa en AM)","guid":"xuFQOtD6TYGDEy3S1e-stQ","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"4","text":"Lacunar (pequeño vaso): 20%","guid":"0_qQZK_PTzabGUXFq2q5Cw","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"4","text":"Otras causas determinadas: 5%","guid":"gd_I2mRWQbigzhun_EiItw","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"4","text":"Criptogénico: 25%","guid":"fH9T6eDRRHamxSkASeS01w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"ACV hemorrágico (15-20%)","guid":"2lFSvSGESZuUwflVq_87ww","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"→ Hemorragia intracerebral (HIC): 10-15%","guid":"zUVG-_UfR36gJs-gNXyhyg","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"→ Hemorragia subaracnoidea (HSA): 3-5%","guid":"OgCnJr06Sxqe9oEIlY2JCQ","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"→ EN AM: HIC asociada a angiopatía amiloide cerebral","guid":"JDI4qcHTSqKO4eUB7ZOvew","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"1","text":"AIT (Ataque Isquémico Transitorio)","guid":"SXtb8WMSRnehC6Rsyrbojg","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"→ Déficit neurológico focal <24h SIN infarto en imagen","guid":"HM95lUFSQ4aJakLqIzfzEg","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"→ ABCD2 score para estratificación","guid":"FXhNbCmoQl2asTmFyNgW9w","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"→ PERLA: AIT en AM = urgencia → riesgo ACV 10-15% a 90 días sin tratamiento","guid":"LzAm9urRQZeqvDkRnyjQUQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"0","text":"EPIDEMIOLOGÍA","guid":"1HZ5PjwISGeGo23lPVEbWQ","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"2ª causa de muerte mundial, 1ª causa de discapacidad","guid":"MxhR2e-HRpei9vjU-639Cw","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"EN ADULTO MAYOR","guid":"pFMWajL2Rs259GGm8oGQ5w","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"→ Incidencia se duplica cada década >55 años","guid":"F-Pu7xRgRcmA8iXCtXB6Hw","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"→ >70% de ACV ocurre en >65 años","guid":"I7zX-2PFSr2-Wi43csTiow","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"20","text":"→ FA no valvular: prevalencia 10% en >80 años → principal FR cardioembólico","guid":"2szg1a6pRaiQ6H2QyB1YMA","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"20","text":"→ Mortalidad 30 días: 10-15% general vs 25-30% en >80 años","guid":"21lcFu4vS-CuYpIYVVJgZA","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"20","text":"→ Recuperación funcional más lenta y menor","guid":"SBDB-04RRQSctVpxe630TQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"0","text":"PRESENTACIÓN CLÍNICA EN URGENCIAS","guid":"-KSXzSAIS9uWcMmLhzt9sA","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Déficits neurológicos focales de inicio súbito","guid":"R04LOxyHRGaWVjHQ-bHOMw","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"→ Hemiparesia/hemiplejia","guid":"91oln5HwQi2xRvXlr_ILTQ","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"→ Afasia (Broca, Wernicke, global)","guid":"0N-IEyA1StaXRxtd84G39w","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"→ Disartria","guid":"1t42-1sCTc-_WgWghHPw5w","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"27","text":"→ Hemianopsia","guid":"mT_PbpofS_6VXZo0rjFEcA","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"27","text":"→ Neglect (hemisferio no dominante)","guid":"QHRPEzkQRHO3PxdbNzEg_g","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"27","text":"→ Ataxia, vértigo, diplopia (circulación posterior)","guid":"FrZqfSkLRMyw_kEKItoOFQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"26","text":"Escala NIHSS (MANDATORIO al ingreso)","guid":"H1oMEo8QQ7CjCrYvZ4Antg","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"→ 0-4: leve","guid":"XCt3vjJwQ-ef_DS4kkx85Q","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"→ 5-15: moderado","guid":"TGXkbeDJTe6v2dmA7ldvyQ","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"34","text":"→ 16-20: moderado-severo","guid":"iohEI2tDTqiQVKS5GgU7kw","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"34","text":"→ 21-42: severo","guid":"67sTEAraQVS2B4c1A_jHPw","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"34","text":"→ Repetir a las 24h y al alta","guid":"bWwbZnc1SASHPbr9ETMefg","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"26","text":"PRESENTACIÓN ATÍPICA EN ADULTO MAYOR","guid":"AV2MokCySiaYn_Zof7CUmg","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"→ Delirium como presentación principal","guid":"z7WDTF33Q9Obqs4B2bXVaA","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"→ Caída sin causa aparente","guid":"L5EKb3MqRAqFGNqYoVs74A","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"40","text":"→ Deterioro funcional agudo sin déficit focal evidente","guid":"8aeck178RpmvHXfbbj6nRA","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"40","text":"→ Síntomas fluctuantes (simulan delirium)","guid":"W8nH7eA0RyOeXgMZYQhUiA","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"40","text":"→ Déficit posterior: vértigo aislado → confundido con VPPB","guid":"7BBBJAsuRQWNvq_OTT018A","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"40","text":"→ PERLA: Vértigo + cefalea + déficit neurológico = ACV posterior hasta demostrar lo contrario","guid":"00kj_5WURMCPcQbgVMEq1w","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"26","text":"Diagnóstico diferencial","guid":"7RRnNX6NSPGXcXQlb_W5Wg","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"→ Hipoglicemia (DESCARTAR PRIMERO → HGT STAT)","guid":"ru9zgljQQ6et1iYcbH8wwg","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"→ Crisis epiléptica (parálisis de Todd)","guid":"4HMbKSuLRZGJaZ3dXOpO9A","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"→ Migraña con aura","guid":"TERTw6KYRz2O40Jvt5xY_Q","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"47","text":"→ Tumor cerebral","guid":"gDhWAiHCT9ikWuZyMqELmw","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"47","text":"→ Hematoma subdural (frecuente en AM anticoagulados)","guid":"4XyR56fNSEePaAiTD5N57Q","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"47","text":"→ Encefalopatía hipertensiva","guid":"JWbnZUbPQKGTBqEgJ1yaxQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"0","text":"EVALUACIÓN INICIAL — CÓDIGO STROKE","guid":"px0WR7hYRSywnwPDjg7hUA","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"Tiempo es cerebro → door-to-CT <25 min","guid":"PDisF6MfSU6x_bxzmwA82Q","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"ABC + estabilización","guid":"JvHGd4FzRRGcPcW5TMbGGg","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"→ Vía aérea permeable (Glasgow ≤8 → IOT)","guid":"Me5qESorR1a0aJM8OIghBA","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"→ PA: NO bajar excepto si >220/120 (isquémico) o pre-trombólisis >185/110","guid":"bDZCt5UxTTi2WsotFtnJRw","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"56","text":"→ Oxígeno solo si SpO2 <94%","guid":"tqqxA5pdTtCQk1PK8xQ5kg","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"56","text":"→ Glicemia: corregir hipo/hiperglicemia severa","guid":"ynsuOTYJQP61jEhFBs2B7A","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"54","text":"TC cerebro SIN contraste (INMEDIATO)","guid":"qC09Hn3KSWSNqe3OywCcCQ","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"→ Descartar hemorragia","guid":"-bR3js9oS2q0YSoQm4tJ6A","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"→ Signos precoces isquemia: borramiento surcos, hiperdensidad ACM","guid":"rI0-sz2rTJi_h6xc6XRMbw","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"→ ASPECTS score (>7 = favorable para trombólisis)","guid":"x19RIvdaRc-Pen8yugExdg","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"54","text":"AngioTC cerebral + cervical","guid":"mnEJkJcfSripIkZ495sVbA","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"→ Identificar oclusión de gran vaso (LVO)","guid":"6-hJjmlMQzWYCC-zouXN9Q","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"→ Si LVO → candidato a trombectomía mecánica","guid":"IeonBIsgRD6tGarmdpa2XQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"54","text":"Laboratorio urgente","guid":"fRbadj5jQxevnuYhNYPZsA","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"→ HGT (ANTES de tPA)","guid":"MlN_KdKjQIaIVbDk2j33sA","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"→ Hemograma, coagulación (INR, TTPa)","guid":"4kjYZXafRMSO12L0q3nUqA","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"→ Troponina (FA + SCA concomitante frecuente)","guid":"aKxEidNxSCW3drpjHoSm7w","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"68","text":"→ Función renal, electrolitos","guid":"o15ePEH1RoCpGXtD0m5XRQ","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"68","text":"→ NO esperar resultados para iniciar tPA (excepto HGT e INR si sospecha anticoagulación)","guid":"nuXTu8n1Tk2kZV5kN6ytNg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"74","parent":"0","text":"MANEJO — ACV ISQUÉMICO","guid":"-OhefwszTkS_fDhu0RUsnQ","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"TROMBÓLISIS IV (Alteplase / Tenecteplase)","guid":"JAot_TafSraB2fys3I-Cxw","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"Alteplase (rt-PA) 0.9 mg/kg (máx 90 mg)","guid":"-YqD5yZ7T8yCfWu71Yn3ZA","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"→ 10% bolo en 1 min, 90% en infusión 60 min","guid":"BCI85yqmQAyt-kk4ICMsHA","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"→ Ventana: <4.5 horas desde inicio síntomas","guid":"sFzA6GObSzak1zHuR6CPdg","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"75","text":"Tenecteplase 0.25 mg/kg (máx 25 mg)","guid":"YLP1sOohR16lrAe5sbNCUA","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"→ Bolo único IV","guid":"uiW3xaHXSk-rT10WG1Yt2Q","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"→ Preferido si LVO y trombectomía planificada (AcT-TNK trial)","guid":"vrDrhRm-RWeh8awlJOcF0A","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"79","text":"→ EN AM: Tenecteplase en bolo único = más práctico","guid":"nZkqXyDBRGqtKh2pTtKDwA","children":[]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"75","text":"Criterios de inclusión","guid":"Mjk278TuSpOXQimzFyCULQ","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"→ ACV isquémico con déficit medible","guid":"x4s7n1xWRpG_-_nFv5uUmg","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"→ Inicio síntomas <4.5h (o <9h con imagen avanzada: DWI/FLAIR mismatch)","guid":"7nH738uzSV2nEdj-JoTW9w","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"83","text":"→ Sin hemorragia en TC","guid":"537fb7uOQT-xLVazBJ2z8w","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"75","text":"Criterios de exclusión relevantes en AM","guid":"s69cfzikQxqkQbl50mv0ag","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"→ INR >1.7 o plaquetas <100.000","guid":"FGhyYxrgSEuOQ3cbLlPRBw","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"87","text":"→ Anticoagulación: HBPM <24h, DOAC <48h (o nivel anti-Xa elevado)","guid":"Rxcql5PKTra_sMttC_bqvA","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"87","text":"→ Cirugía mayor <14 días","guid":"WV39sXxzReuecxjphIW9aQ","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"87","text":"→ ACV previo <3 meses","guid":"SlK22BYURhCvWhuZc-1qVA","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"87","text":"→ PERLA: Edad >80 NO es contraindicación absoluta para tPA (IST-3, 2012)","guid":"_T2jbfRLQn29l_6Zlzjj3g","children":[]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"75","text":"PA pre y post trombólisis","guid":"sDQL5sT2RNyf6CQIYrW72g","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"→ Pre: <185/110 para iniciar","guid":"LNnxjHhmR8mE-v4fIlbl5w","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"→ Post: <180/105 por 24h","guid":"zPO8LHZuQjO1iZWd8cLZMQ","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"93","text":"→ Labetalol 10-20 mg IV o Nicardipino infusión","guid":"V3ETfmheSTiVaA_CRviY6Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"74","text":"TROMBECTOMÍA MECÁNICA (LVO)","guid":"9NniPdBRRcS_LnjoNjDQgA","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"→ Oclusión de gran vaso: ACI terminal, M1, basilar proximal","guid":"AABHMd-WSZejTHS0Xr7yRw","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"→ Ventana: <6h estándar, <24h con imagen favorable (DAWN, DEFUSE-3)","guid":"O-UWkfAMSJCFApkFAoRtPg","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"97","text":"→ NIHSS ≥6 + ASPECTS ≥6","guid":"M-LXFO28Tt-r87mkvWctpw","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"97","text":"→ EN AM: Beneficio demostrado hasta >80 años (HERMES meta-análisis)","guid":"6y3bGBAxTNWHhgevQIIVVA","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"97","text":"→ CFS como factor en decisión, no edad cronológica","guid":"GwCqBLBCQ9q49G60xDl7ag","children":[]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"74","text":"Manejo post-tPA / post-trombectomía","guid":"629z06GFSAC8DDqvmiHqJQ","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"→ NIHSS cada 15 min x 2h, luego c/30 min x 6h, luego c/1h x 16h","guid":"7d5ZKoxRR3-jw2WxOpXc1g","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"→ PA cada 15 min x 2h","guid":"aOWJn9BATm6xr7E6rWWxtA","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"103","text":"→ TC control a las 24h antes de iniciar antiagregación","guid":"WqzTOUs6RUardyySwNJqFQ","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"103","text":"→ NO antiagregantes ni anticoagulantes en primeras 24h post-tPA","guid":"nRFo_28tStK_EKc4s40v9g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"0","text":"MANEJO — ACV HEMORRÁGICO","guid":"ffswqXBWTxa5m9FvGvqr8A","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"Hemorragia intracerebral (HIC)","guid":"u1i8tkzgSYinXnl6p2wWdA","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"→ Control PA: meta <140 mmHg sistólica en <1h (INTERACT2, ATACH-2)","guid":"CEbtDbkSSeKnZom6cxX3LQ","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"109","text":"→ Nicardipino IV o Labetalol IV","guid":"8rHQSB8_T0C8K7AY5kiJrw","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"109","text":"→ Reversión anticoagulación URGENTE","guid":"RdRPwm2ORtOKMN1wV7rL5g","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"TACO (Warfarina): Vitamina K 10 mg IV + CCP 4 factores (preferido sobre PFC)","guid":"57ajeGLiThygV-wC8uLvCg","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"DOAC (Dabigatrán): Idarucizumab 5g IV","guid":"vPxQ8bD6SRmj-y5WkOgoUA","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"DOAC (Rivaroxabán/Apixabán): Andexanet alfa o CCP 4 factores","guid":"OjydK4i7RIGQzeuDsnQXnQ","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"112","text":"Heparina: Protamina","guid":"nHUGKcsHTKW7H_dV91YL7A","children":[]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"109","text":"→ Plaquetas si <100.000 y cirugía planificada","guid":"X_YzC8IdS3iwunjJATQYnA","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"109","text":"→ Neurocirugía: evaluar si hematoma >30 mL, hidrocefalia, herniación","guid":"i-hYUv7QRmy1rFq_PjyjAw","children":[]}]},{"id":"119","parent":"108","text":"HSA","guid":"PqqB51klQS2OkwaDRaf1hA","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"→ TC cerebro (sensibilidad >95% <6h)","guid":"98JoJqKGTPGW4GsICif4Qw","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"119","text":"→ Si TC negativa + alta sospecha → PL (xantocromía)","guid":"NnN_jgsnT9WDoN9UlPjihA","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"119","text":"→ AngioTC o angiografía para identificar aneurisma","guid":"B_UILsoCRw6m8H1F0X6g0w","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"119","text":"→ Nimodipino 60 mg c/4h VO x 21 días (prevención vasoespasmo)","guid":"oOU_bUHDRdWzcfubYNUfRQ","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"119","text":"→ Derivar a neurocirugía/neurorradiología","guid":"LDyO67AmS5aLyo09Dpwwaw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"0","text":"CONSIDERACIONES GERIÁTRICAS ESPECÍFICAS","guid":"v3vhFxsjRHG_XS2XE2jvhA","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"FA y cardioembolia","guid":"o2IPUbCASGaRTgCRqerXqw","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"→ FA = causa #1 de ACV en >80 años","guid":"yRFb-EaQS9CeIAg9pJQaUQ","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"→ CHA2DS2-VASc: edad 65-74 = +1, ≥75 = +2","guid":"0yUGs0H4R2eF-T99vy10tQ","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"126","text":"→ Anticoagulación: DOAC preferido sobre Warfarina en AM (menor HIC)","guid":"Xc_uz37tRb2sikFTrn4GlA","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"126","text":"→ HAS-BLED para evaluar riesgo sangrado","guid":"AqMlP4O8QemBMMe4NuphJA","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"126","text":"→ PERLA: Beneficio de anticoagulación AUMENTA con la edad (mayor riesgo embolico)","guid":"3DLR9czQTXGlcFYgkSkcJA","children":[]}]},{"id":"132","parent":"125","text":"Fragilidad y decisiones terapéuticas","guid":"McaHUjzDQWGvHvG5fOXW0g","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"→ CFS al ingreso","guid":"uYarBJ6kT5yfwrv7SXFIbg","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"132","text":"→ CFS ≥7 → trombectomía: evaluar caso a caso (beneficio incierto)","guid":"YnSlowOASGaHkRc5IOWmtg","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"132","text":"→ Paciente previamente independiente → tratar agresivamente independiente de edad","guid":"B7HDRiGEQR6wiJz7Ribc7g","children":[]}]},{"id":"136","parent":"125","text":"Disfagia","guid":"ONCPbKmpRQmDyuYLctIJUA","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"→ Screening OBLIGATORIO antes de alimentación oral","guid":"j8q4FIikRZS9gKjoByiaoA","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"→ Test del vaso de agua o evaluación fonoaudiológica formal","guid":"WghRE9sTQgu4cml287IXvg","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"136","text":"→ Neumonía aspirativa = principal causa muerte post-ACV en AM","guid":"4Ng0Y1VkSF27rPWRvOqgHA","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"136","text":"→ SNG si disfagia severa >48h","guid":"l7VCXeQ_Q2Sj0Oc21VQUSg","children":[]}]},{"id":"141","parent":"125","text":"Rehabilitación precoz","guid":"-AA5i3HZS4CvHBO6ZSEx1g","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"→ Movilización a las 24-48h (AVERT: no ultrainicial <24h)","guid":"yjjAWOM3QwKwuysCUp5tVw","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"141","text":"→ Evaluación funcional: Barthel, mRS al ingreso y al alta","guid":"PCnO-5GRQtKoq4b3SRt5SQ","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"141","text":"→ Kinesioterapia motora + fonoaudiología + TO","guid":"T0MDD1NHRv2a7_wTB6Qjew","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"141","text":"→ Prevención deterioro funcional intrahospitalario","guid":"Hv3_OiffTSyrd1ukJS_TOg","children":[]}]},{"id":"146","parent":"125","text":"Prevención secundaria","guid":"G7AtnwaoSYydvowEZPnjYg","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"→ Antiagregación: AAS 100 mg/día (o Clopidogrel)","guid":"G3AuIJ0jSw2NUxWE7s5TKQ","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"146","text":"→ Si FA: DOAC (Apixabán 5 mg c/12h; 2.5 mg si ≥2 de: edad ≥80, peso ≤60 kg, Cr ≥1.5)","guid":"X7JwLMxXS9mlIX-oumSdnQ","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"146","text":"→ Estatina alta intensidad","guid":"SdULmXRrS4GhJb_JjAyXfg","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"146","text":"→ Control HTA: meta <130/80 (SPRINT)","guid":"KW_XjTwtRzeyBi-IDa2mEA","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"146","text":"→ EN AM: Inicio gradual antihipertensivos, evitar hipotensión ortostática","guid":"6O9ae3rpQd6n5XD4s_RwZA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"0","text":"PERLAS CLÍNICAS MUE","guid":"l0ebS2oYQLS0eWgl1GpIUg","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"→ HGT es lo PRIMERO → hipoglicemia simula ACV","guid":"D9nYZ84QR9aORYKJ-PvR7w","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"→ Door-to-CT <25 min, door-to-needle <60 min (tPA)","guid":"QBlbI_AzSUS4xuD6k5pS6w","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"→ Edad >80 NO excluye trombólisis ni trombectomía","guid":"irjZOBu-RfKbtqCNwG4CJA","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"152","text":"→ Tenecteplase en bolo único reemplazando Alteplase (evidencia creciente)","guid":"e_GVrcaDR9-LoNYmtAf1sw","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"152","text":"→ Vértigo aislado en AM + FDR vascular = ACV posterior hasta demostrar lo contrario","guid":"oS8yQqPoS-Gb4fGBcYMHWw","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"152","text":"→ FA en >80 años: anticoagular SIEMPRE salvo CI absoluta → beneficio > riesgo","guid":"vXiBL4AJShCaZp8kea459g","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"152","text":"→ Screening disfagia ANTES de comer → neumonía aspirativa = causa #1 muerte post-ACV en AM","guid":"N_yeCVYtQveo7DBkspI9nw","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"152","text":"→ ASPECTS >7 = favorable para reperfusión","guid":"iIXRDKCCRoyIQPbabgatuA","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"152","text":"→ DAWN/DEFUSE-3: ventana trombectomía hasta 24h con imagen favorable","guid":"DYQSoW_lSS6DVUy-Z7P4dg","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"152","text":"→ Delirium puede ser la PRESENTACIÓN de un ACV en adulto mayor","guid":"3s98LV37Q5OvMczC8l0FZg","children":[]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"0","text":"LR DIAGNOSTICOS","guid":"JRFrI4itTdyDoH1w3zTd8g","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"HALLAZGOS CLINICOS (cabecera)","guid":"pYhxLLaxSRaPVBTiw0ES-g","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"Cincinnati Prehospital Stroke Scale (cualquier +) -> LR+ 5.5 -> LR- 0.39 -> PMID:15900010","guid":"qzYhH51zRXeKeZS7LuiMOA","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"164","text":"Facial droop (paresia facial) -> LR+ 4.9 -> LR- 0.62 -> PMID:15900010","guid":"2CvbiCOGRtGdowDGOzzfbg","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"164","text":"Arm drift (pronator drift) -> LR+ 4.3 -> LR- 0.62 -> PMID:15900010","guid":"UdnuTad0R8CcMXDGaVYI1A","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"164","text":"Disartria / habla anormal -> LR+ 4.5 -> LR- 0.54 -> PMID:15900010","guid":"X6zakK_VQ-WsVRkQxaddTQ","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"164","text":"Hemianopsia -> LR+ 3.0 -> LR- NR -> PMID:15900010","guid":"x_DjotJfTn6TXDje4XblgA","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"164","text":"Debilidad aguda MMII unilateral -> LR+ 5.2 -> LR- NR -> PMID:15900010","guid":"-QjLpSAqRNatUDVgOw8tCQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"171","parent":"163","text":"SCORE / REGLA CLINICA","guid":"AOXi3MInQQuSR0qeqeIaQg","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"ROSIER score >0 -> LR+ 6.0 -> LR- 0.30 -> PMID:16239179","guid":"M5N4iFwERd-vLJVmhkBHGA","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"171","text":"LAPSS (Los Angeles) positivo -> LR+ 31 -> LR- 0.09 -> PMID:10625718","guid":"CVNrU0KSSmymOSNp8wKbEA","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"171","text":"FAST (cualquier componente +) -> LR+ 4.3 -> LR- 0.17 -> PMID:12511753","guid":"5w5N_v2QQeGez6Od6jKKqw","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"171","text":"MEND exam positivo -> LR+ ~5 -> LR- ~0.2 -> PMID:15900010","guid":"axNdJ9a2Rk6j_WFpZs4FHA","children":[]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"163","text":"NIHSS (uso severidad, no diagnostico)","guid":"dX8GwkK5QFuIA6BfGSYACQ","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"NIHSS 0-5 -> leve","guid":"fLMgQtovRgeDJjKMhrW3Pw","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"176","text":"NIHSS 6-15 -> moderado","guid":"RoeZ_RkdT4aaaSGxBeSP0A","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"176","text":"NIHSS 16-20 -> moderado-severo","guid":"-MYcAcJOSwWygTYAksAi3Q","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"176","text":"NIHSS >20 -> severo","guid":"AyL8OzOeSkCUkyjt7dwPWQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"181","parent":"163","text":"HALLAZGOS IMAGEN","guid":"gjg7Z2z2SOqF0AF3mhfWxA","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"TC sin contraste para HEMORRAGIA (primera prioridad) -> LR+ muy alto, LR- bajo (gold standard inicial) -> (guias AHA 2019)","guid":"WwGRvbkPRieJ4w_WfWlybg","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"181","text":"RM DWI para ISQUEMIA aguda <24h -> Sens 99% / Esp 92% -> PMID:17258712","guid":"3zY8ckLUTG6ClIwdl3KRwg","children":[]}]},{"id":"184","parent":"163","text":"INTERPRETACION","guid":"2yyeSspdQo2XQR78tpdUMw","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"LR+ >10 o LR- <0.1 -> cambio GRANDE","guid":"fyu3kKnuSdCCA-VX1fcDlA","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"184","text":"LR+ 5-10 o LR- 0.1-0.2 -> cambio MODERADO","guid":"MszoiZ5ZRTKFcSv9yNRYfQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"187","parent":"163","text":"GERIATRIA","guid":"qttqegyZTy6W7XPqwdHctw","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"Dx diferencial critico -> delirium, hipoglicemia, crisis HTA, postictal","guid":"28cTiEDmRtizjVjz4buLzg","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"187","text":"Ventana tPA <4.5h / trombectomia <24h - sin limite de edad","guid":"E1USUlX7TXKrPtsxHoyyrA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"190","parent":"0","text":"REFERENCIAS","guid":"Yma1-es1Q22TY2WdniauNw","children":[{"id":"191","parent":"190","text":"→ Powers WJ et al. AHA/ASA Stroke Guidelines 2019. Stroke. 2019;50:e344-e418","guid":"l_0q3K4ETyWBGFe22BVw3w","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"190","text":"→ Berge E et al. ESO Guidelines Stroke 2021. Eur Stroke J. 2021;6(1):I-LXII","guid":"ZP9J5FiqQLO8TEQXf3KjKw","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"190","text":"→ Goyal M et al. HERMES meta-analysis. Lancet. 2016;387:1723-1731","guid":"RQeCn4-HRdmjta-ir9GOyA","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"190","text":"→ Nogueira RG et al. DAWN trial. NEJM. 2018;378:11-21","guid":"3OQ4DfSYQO2AQzXlERex-A","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"190","text":"→ Albers GW et al. DEFUSE-3. NEJM. 2018;378:708-718","guid":"Ym2P23iWSFSKjUjMacwmCg","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"190","text":"→ IST-3 Collaborative Group. tPA in elderly. Lancet. 2012;379:2352-2363","guid":"AoCDBkRyTRGpHgGcyKhV4A","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"190","text":"→ Menon BK et al. AcT-TNK trial. Lancet. 2022;400:161-169","guid":"pCo9MhhCSaex-15ZERdUqA","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"190","text":"→ Anderson CS et al. INTERACT2. NEJM. 2013;368:2355-2365","guid":"M_LPfNU9RHmjjyWzKRd3XA","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":198,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"MUE - Medicina de Urgencia","filename":"MUE_ACV_Stroke","id":"map_2496","resolved_references":[]}